General.Name: StasyQ
General.Description:
StasyQ is a unique platform for adult content. The portal has been functioning since 2015 and is a live streaming website for erotic models. 

SQOIN was designed so that users could make fully anonymous transactions with no fees and allows models, producers another way to monetize their content.

StasyCoin(SQOIN) is an ERC20 compliant token and smart contract system, based on Ethereum Network.

ICO.Description:
StasyQ is a unique platform for adult content. The portal has been functioning since 2015 and is a live streaming website for erotic models. 

SQOIN was designed so that users could make fully anonymous transactions with no fees and allows models, producers another way to monetize their content.

StasyCoin(SQOIN) is an ERC20 compliant token and smart contract system, based on Ethereum Network.

Team:

  • Romanas Stelmokaitis: CEO & CTO. 
  • Vadim Khodakov: Digital Producer. 
  • Vitali Gisko: Lead Product Designer. 
  • Alex Pankevich: Digital Producer & Strategist. 
  • Aleksej Tisionok: Designer. 
  • Seva Savko: Media Manager. 

StasyQ will be holding its ICO on April 4th, 2018. The ICO token supply represents 70% of the total token supply, so there will be a total of 245000000 tokens available, for 0.00006896551 ETH each during the offering. The ICO funding cap is 20,000 ETH and is expected to end on May 5th, 2018 or when the funding cap is reached. All unsold tokens will be burned.  StasyQ ICO will feature a bounty, and the token will not be mineable.

Token Reserve Split (30%):

  • 25% Team;
  • 5% PR, Bounties;

Fund Distribution:

  • 60% Marketing;
  • 20% Development;
  • 15% Operational;
  • 5% Legal;
